Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.59,0:00:09.11,Default,Gang,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you think people avoid \Nus when we come through?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:11.43,Default,Gang,0000,0000,0000,,You're just too intimidating.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.43,0:00:12.68,Default,Gang,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.68,0:00:15.03,Default,Gang,0000,0000,0000,,But we aren't doing anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:19.45,Default,Gang,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah... I heard there's a real \Nintimidating guy at Shuuei High, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:21.13,Default,Gang,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I've heard of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.13,0:00:25.17,Default,Gang,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who saw him said he's over two \Nmeters tall, like a new species of bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:29.36,Default,Gang,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he almost killed someone \Nright in front of the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:30.67,Default,Gang,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.67,0:00:35.17,Default,Gang,0000,0000,0000,,That's only a rumor. \NPeople keep exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.17,0:00:36.97,Default,Gang,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like an urban legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:38.66,Default,Gang,0000,0000,0000,,Right, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.66,0:00:40.06,Default,Gang,0000,0000,0000,,No way he's two meters tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:42.49,Default,Gang,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and a new bear species? Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:49.06,Default - italics,Gang,0000,0000,0000,,I saw an urban legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.06,0:00:50.75,Default - italics,Sign 0052,0000,0000,0000,,He's totally over two meters tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.06,0:00:53.23,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0052,0000,0000,0000,,AHHHHH
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.75,0:00:51.34,Default - italics,Sign 0052,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:52.06,Default - italics,Sign 0052,0000,0000,0000,,He saw me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.06,0:00:52.89,Default - italics,Sign 0052,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna strangle me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.89,0:00:54.20,Default - italics,Sign 0052,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna eat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:56.04,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:57.53,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I arrived just now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.89,0:01:01.04,Default - italics,Gang,0000,0000,0000,,The urban legend has a girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:36.17,Title1,Sign 0232,0000,0000,0000,,My Christmas
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.37,0:02:35.08,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Gouda Takeo, a first-year in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.08,0:02:36.17,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's now winter,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:38.30,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,but I still feel like I'm in spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:39.55,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,And soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:42.07,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be Christmas soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:43.05,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:45.81,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas... With Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:47.46,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takeo-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.46,0:02:52.19,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,About Christmas... Can we celebrate \Nwith my friends and yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:55.76,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,No one seems to have any plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.76,0:02:57.69,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas with everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:02:58.93,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:03:00.45,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I hadn't thought of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.97,0:03:03.75,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea. Okay, let's do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:04.80,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:06.19,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.19,0:03:08.83,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already a happy man, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:11.83,Class,Sign 0310,0000,0000,0000,,Class 1-6
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.74,0:03:11.83,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, a Christmas party with girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:13.09,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be a first for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:16.59,SFX-BlueBlue,Sign 0314,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFEFAE4&\an9}The day has finally come!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:14.21,Default,Kakiya,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be my first time since elementary school!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:16.59,Default,Fudo,0000,0000,0000,,This year, I won't have to walk \Nthrough the streets, crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:18.14,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Long live, Yamato-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:19.71,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,What a goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:22.75,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato, they're super happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.75,0:03:23.59,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:27.68,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna, you should come, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:29.10,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:29.93,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:32.37,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.37,0:03:33.57,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Um, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:37.86,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Can I tell Nanako-chan at that Christmas thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:40.08,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:40.80,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Tell her what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:43.86,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Well, tell her that I want to ask her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:43.86,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0343,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(443,1)}C'mon, read between the lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:45.45,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Since when?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:46.37,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,So, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.84,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:51.50,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Should we ask Yamato for permission, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:53.30,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we should.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:54.47,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Please do that, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.47,0:03:56.63,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see, he likes her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:03:59.43,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you'll be happy together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:00.76,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Give it your best shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:03.76,Phone,Sign 0402,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Inbox \N\NFrom: Takeo-kun \NTo: Yamato Rinko \NSubject: Christmas \N\NIt's all good. \NEveryone's happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:04.45,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun and his friends are on for Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:06.19,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Rinko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.19,0:04:07.91,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's exchange gifts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:09.06,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,A thousand-yen budget?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:10.27,Default,Mana,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go karaoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:11.92,Default,Kojima,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:12.98,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Rinko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:16.52,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kurihara-kun coming, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:19.00,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Kurihara-kun? I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:20.06,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try asking right now—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:21.54,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't have to ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:23.63,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:25.28,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Rinko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:31.54,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,What does it mean if a guy \Ntries to hold your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:32.53,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.53,0:04:34.55,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that mean he likes you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:36.36,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'd think.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.37,0:04:40.55,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:44.12,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Kurihara asked for my contact info,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:47.82,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,and we went to a movie once...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:52.57,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,And he held my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.57,0:04:53.56,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:56.40,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0455,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(233,354)\an7}Huh? Huh? I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:57.00,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Um, doesn't that mean he likes you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:58.91,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can't be sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.91,0:05:00.80,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't said anything definite.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:01.80,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:04.50,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,If he didn't like you a little, he wouldn't \Nhave asked you to the movies!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:09.11,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel about Kurihara-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.11,0:05:09.70,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:11.36,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.36,0:05:14.12,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,If he asked, I guess I could go out with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:16.86,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Anything I can do to help?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.86,0:05:17.33,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:18.21,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.92,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to ask Takeo-kun about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:21.92,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:24.42,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,What should I get as a present?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:26.80,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I need to work more hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:29.43,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Takeo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:31.68,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.01,0:05:34.43,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:39.52,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,So a reservation for twelve, \Non December 24th, at 4 PM?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:40.32,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:42.05,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:43.44,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:46.68,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,There's a big Christmas tree in the courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:49.36,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:52.86,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the Christmas tree can \Nbe seen from all the rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:55.04,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,It's even better at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:57.29,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and there's a story about that tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:06:00.96,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,At the very top, there's one star \Nthat's different from the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:02.55,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:02.96,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:05.07,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You can see it all the way \Nfrom here, Takeo-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:06.84,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(421,474)} Wow
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:09.47,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,If you pluck that star and ask someone out,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.94,0:06:10.94,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,they'll say yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.94,0:06:14.08,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's cold and your hands go numb, \Nso you can't really climb up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:15.66,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,It's high and scary,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:18.63,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,so no one's ever managed it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.63,0:06:21.44,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I think you might be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:23.98,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't need it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:28.36,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,So, you have your reservation,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:30.36,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,but which karaoke room would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.19,0:06:33.48,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,That star should grant someone else's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.48,0:06:34.49,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Um, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:38.50,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so looking forward to Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.93,0:06:42.89,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,We've all been talking about how we'd \Nlike to exchange gifts and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:43.88,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:48.12,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, is Kurihara-kun coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.12,0:06:48.88,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:51.72,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is Nanako-san coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:52.64,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:54.89,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0653,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good.                               Okay, okay
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:05.85,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't hold hands with someone \Nunless you liked them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:06.90,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:10.79,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Right, I should check in with Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:12.03,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0711,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Thanks~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.79,0:07:12.03,Default - flashback,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:16.15,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato, Kurihara said he likes Nanako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.15,0:07:17.03,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.03,0:07:19.49,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,He'd like to ask her out on Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.49,0:07:20.16,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:22.08,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:24.42,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give them plenty of \Nopportunities to be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:26.34,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:28.17,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let's help them out as best we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:29.96,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:29.96,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:31.43,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Kurihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.29,0:07:34.18,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be a merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:35.76,SignB,Sign 0736,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas with Nanako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:40.31,SFX-BlueBlue,Sign 0736,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Kurihara
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:36.46,SignB,Sign 0737,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas with Nanako-chan. \N\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.46,0:07:38.57,SignB,Sign 0737,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas with Nanako-chan. \N\N\NYeah. \N\N\NI'm over the Moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:49.07,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:50.82,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:57.20,Default,Kuuri,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Nanako-chan, aren't you \Ncold with bare legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:02.29,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:03.21,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice and big.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:04.65,Default,Kaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:06.46,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.51,0:08:08.79,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.79,0:08:10.96,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,There's a huge Christmas tree in the courtyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:16.55,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Toward the top of the tree, there's this \None star that's different from the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:19.48,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,They say if you take that star \Nand then ask someone out,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:21.06,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,the person will say yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:22.55,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:24.97,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,That's way too high!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:26.62,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,How many meters is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:31.77,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you think that \Nonly Takeo could get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.90,0:08:37.86,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako, can I sit next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:40.21,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu, sit here with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:41.78,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:51.50,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I'm sitting next to Nanako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:52.26,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:56.99,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:58.80,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:10.13,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako-chan, I can pass you \Nanything you want to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:11.16,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:13.32,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, let me pour it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:14.78,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:17.10,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,He's meticulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.10,0:09:19.37,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I should try to learn from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.57,0:09:23.07,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yamato?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:25.15,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:27.50,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't like spicy food...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:29.77,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It was spicier than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:30.87,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eat it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.87,0:09:31.92,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.92,0:09:32.55,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:36.42,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:39.05,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Is this an indirect kiss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:40.25,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:41.06,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.49,0:09:47.23,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo and Yamato-san make such a good pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:50.48,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Do you ever think about wanting \Na boyfriend, Nanako-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:51.84,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:53.62,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sure, like any other girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.62,0:09:55.69,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you have high standards!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:09:58.62,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,I think they're normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:09:59.94,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:01.67,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,I bet they're sky high!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.67,0:10:03.74,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,They're normal. What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:03.74,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Kurihara...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:05.77,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's he going on about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:07.75,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he going to ask her out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:10.13,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't we go see the Christmas tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:11.94,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the courtyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:13.50,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:16.47,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to create a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:18.07,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,So pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:21.55,Default,Kaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's much bigger than the one at home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:23.24,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,You guys have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:25.30,Default,Kaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it goes up to the ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:27.20,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Can I come see?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:28.02,Default,Fudo,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:29.49,Default,Kaki,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.49,0:10:30.56,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:31.81,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:33.03,Default,Kaki,0000,0000,0000,,The girls can!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:34.01,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:37.15,Default,Mana,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's take a photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:38.28,Default,Kojima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:45.16,Default,Mana,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:47.00,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:50.00,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty, but it's also super cold out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:51.46,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:54.21,Default,Kojima,0000,0000,0000,,Let's exchange presents!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:56.18,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:11:02.21,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! What're you waiting \Nfor, Nanako-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:04.35,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Kurihara...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:06.47,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,What am I to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:07.40,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:09.59,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:12.17,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, close the door already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:13.70,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Um, a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:14.74,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Sorta?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:17.16,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:18.76,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,You'll catch a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:21.99,EyecatchA,Sign 1121,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFAFED0&}Kuri
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:23.49,EyecatchB,Sign 1122,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF48EEC&}Na
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.48,0:11:26.33,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,We put everyone's presents in this \Nbag and tied ribbons to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:28.75,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,so pull one ribbon each!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:31.87,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way to tell who'll get whose present!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:33.32,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.32,0:11:34.75,Default,Kaki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's figure out the drawing order!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:35.96,Default,Kaki,0000,0000,0000,,Should we just do rock-paper-scissors?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:38.01,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,First comes rock...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:40.63,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:42.93,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sunakawa-kun, just pick whichever you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:43.51,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:48.37,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:49.43,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:50.43,Default,Fudo,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:53.10,Default,Kojima,0000,0000,0000,,Um, okay, this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:53.98,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:56.41,SFX-RedBlack,Sign 1154,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\an9}That's Nanako's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:58.03,Default,Kojima,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this one, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:11:59.03,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,I'm next!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:01.63,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Pick this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:02.74,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:05.16,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:05.81,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.81,0:12:06.94,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Is this from Nanako-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.94,0:12:07.95,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:09.54,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,I picked Nanako-chan's gift!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:09.54,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1209,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(207,1)}Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:11.12,Default,Sign 1209,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can I open this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:13.92,Default,Sign 1209,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:15.35,Default,Kaki,0000,0000,0000,,Xavier!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:18.55,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Nanako, you're next.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:20.05,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:22.68,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:27.17,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,That's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:28.53,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,It went to Nanako-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.53,0:12:29.39,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,It's fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:32.59,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:34.02,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Let's sing, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.04,0:12:38.01,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really do songs,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:39.93,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll just be on the tambourine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.93,0:12:42.24,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be on the maracas today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:43.53,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,We're the cheerleaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:48.91,SignA,Sign 1246,0000,0000,0000,,Can't catch up, but I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:47.85,Default,Kaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this song's Kurihara's favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:50.29,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Can one of the girls sing with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:54.05,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako, you're good at this song, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:55.91,Default,Mana,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear Nanako sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.91,0:12:56.67,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:00.03,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the mic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.03,0:13:02.17,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, a duet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:12.89,Default - italics,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,I wish love would work out like sweets, \Nas long as you follow the recipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:14.25,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Nanako-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.97,0:13:23.69,Default - italics,KN,0000,0000,0000,,I wish the distance between us would change \Nwith time, just like meringues do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:25.80,Default,Kojima,0000,0000,0000,,Look this way, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:26.46,Default - italics,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Calm and—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:27.70,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, take our photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:29.61,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,A two-shot with Nanako-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.61,0:13:30.86,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.86,0:13:32.51,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,You're acting all weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:35.25,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:41.50,Default - italics,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Can't catch up, but I want—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:51.01,SignA,Sign 1348,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly, there's a story. Give me an answer. \NThe more clumsy and awkward we are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:53.16,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.49,0:13:59.58,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, shouldn't you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:01.95,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:03.11,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:07.61,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:10.24,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:15.14,Default,Gang,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:16.16,Default,Gang,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:18.19,Default,Gang,0000,0000,0000,,You're here, just the two of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:19.92,Default,Gang,0000,0000,0000,,But it's Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:22.32,Default,Gang,0000,0000,0000,,Come join us in our room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:31.47,Default,Gang,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:34.70,Default,Gang,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've seen her before...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:36.85,Default,Gang,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have we met before?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:40.35,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,This way, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.83,0:14:45.48,Default,Gang,0000,0000,0000,,Right! She's the urban legend's girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:49.27,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:51.46,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:53.38,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, that was scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:55.50,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Nanako-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:14:58.50,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you help me yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:15:00.57,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,I hate that about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.57,0:15:01.75,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:07.76,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:09.72,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:12.64,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try so hard to get us together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:15.26,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Not everyone can be like you guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:20.14,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,all lovey-dovey and head over \Nheels about each other, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.11,0:15:23.15,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:37.29,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:42.29,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I was wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:45.97,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this wasn't helping her at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.97,0:15:49.95,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I should have been more considerate \Nof Nanako's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:51.30,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:52.95,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I was wrong, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:56.61,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,My feelings are my own,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.61,0:15:58.81,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,but that has nothing to do with how others feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.53,0:16:01.81,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything about how they feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:05.31,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I really have to be more careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:10.71,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,We have to learn how to just watch \Nover them without interfering.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:11.83,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.83,0:16:16.48,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Sunakawa-kun did for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.48,0:16:17.67,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Like Suna.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:18.95,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Right, like Sunakawa-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.11,0:16:22.46,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Being kind enough not to do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:26.59,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,To have the heart to watch over them \Nwithout saying anything—that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:29.58,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:30.55,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.28,0:16:34.73,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, for now, let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.12,0:16:38.22,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:42.23,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,how could one of me beat three of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:44.41,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought it'd complicate things
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:45.98,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,and risk getting Nanako-chan hurt
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:49.23,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,or put her in danger, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:50.08,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Be kind enough not to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:51.78,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not that manly,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.83,0:16:53.43,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Have the heart to watch over them \Nwithout saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:53.61,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm not as strong as Takeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.02,0:16:57.99,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I have any confidence that \NI could've talked my way out of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:17:00.49,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,like Sunakawa might have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:03.76,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'm just below average in every way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.13,0:17:03.35,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Be kind enough not to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.76,0:17:05.66,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Watch over them without saying any—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.76,0:17:05.93,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Or even lower, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:08.75,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe she wanted you to help, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:11.26,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't quibble!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:14.26,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.62,0:17:18.60,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything about this now, \Nbut you still can!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.94,0:17:20.57,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:36.24,Phone,Sign 1736,0000,0000,0000,,Incoming Call \NRinko
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.63,0:17:38.08,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Rinko, I'm so sorry about what I said—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:39.37,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:41.93,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako, you should know that Kurihara-kun's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:46.25,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:47.65,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.51,0:17:54.26,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Kurihara?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:57.34,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Kurihara-kun wants \Nto get that star for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:17:58.14,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:01.23,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:02.16,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:03.58,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:04.57,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Kurihara!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.57,0:18:05.38,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,You should stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.38,0:18:06.27,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:08.75,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, quit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:09.90,Default,Kaki,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:11.90,Default,Fudo,0000,0000,0000,,How many times have you already fallen off?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.33,0:18:16.15,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take that star and \Nask Nanako-chan out...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:20.43,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,When Yamato-san told us about the star,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:23.79,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako-chan looked like she \Nwanted that to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:27.89,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,I acted like it was nothing because \NI felt self-conscious about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:31.79,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not strong like Takeo,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:36.67,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,but I do want to show the girl I like \Nwhat I'm capable of as a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:38.61,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Kurihara!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:46.45,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:48.04,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,I got the star!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:10.57,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not strong like Takeo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:13.09,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a pushover, and I tend to \Njust go with the flow,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:15.00,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,but I do like you, Nanako-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:17.76,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Please go out with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:27.02,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not honest about my feelings like Rinko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:28.63,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bake cakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.63,0:19:30.15,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,and I can be hard to get along with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.15,0:19:30.81,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:31.81,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,I like that about you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:34.32,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,I like how you're a pushover, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.56,0:19:41.41,Default,Fudo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, 'grats.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.41,0:19:43.20,Default,Mana,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats, Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:45.03,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,All right, a celebratory toss!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:46.97,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:46.67,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:48.97,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.40,0:19:50.21,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:50.21,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.63,0:19:52.04,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:52.82,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.37,0:19:55.09,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.83,0:19:59.47,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun, this is a separate gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:01.35,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's a stollen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:03.37,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:08.08,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas! Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.08,0:20:09.22,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:11.87,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:13.22,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I love her so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:14.75,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:16.82,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:18.57,Board,Sign 2018,0000,0000,0000,,Closing Ceremony Today
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:22.07,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I always thought she had nice legs,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:25.46,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,but when I just blurted it out \Nduring our skating outing,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.46,0:20:27.29,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,it totally rubbed her the wrong way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:30.08,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,When she looked at me like I was a worm,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:31.92,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,I just fell for her right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:33.08,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.51,0:20:35.19,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,And on the train ride home,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:37.01,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to make any more wrong moves,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.01,0:20:39.02,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,so I'd thrown both hands up in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.02,0:20:43.09,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,She was giving me this wry \Nsmile that was so cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:45.67,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, speak of the devil... It's Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:50.85,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 2047,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs22}"Nanako"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.67,0:20:46.71,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:49.22,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,I was just about to call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.22,0:20:50.85,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, are you watching me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:54.10,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:56.23,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:57.43,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.43,0:20:58.51,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,...Nanako is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:20:59.98,Default,Mana,0000,0000,0000,,...when she has a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.98,0:21:00.76,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.98,0:21:01.41,Default,Kojima,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:01.68,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:02.71,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.06,0:21:06.35,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Osamu said his winter break starts tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.81,0:21:05.44,SFX-BlueBlue,Sign 2105,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\c&HE8F344&}"Osamu"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:07.91,Default - italics,All,0000,0000,0000,,We're all on winter break.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.40,0:21:11.68,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Nanako and Kurihara-kun will \Nhave their first kiss really fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.68,0:21:12.62,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:14.09,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.09,0:21:14.75,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,We already had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:15.37,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:18.01,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,We kissed on our way back from \Nthe Christmas get-together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.01,0:21:20.07,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,He just rushed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.77,0:21:22.09,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,So fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.82,0:21:25.43,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.43,0:21:26.47,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Rinko?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:31.22,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'm just not attractive like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:32.93,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:34.54,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! I can help!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.27,0:21:35.98,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 2135,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(316,1)}All of a sudden, she's acting superior
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:51.01,Title2,Sign 2248,0000,0000,0000,,My Birthday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.82,0:22:49.50,Default - margin,T,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: My Birthday.
